From: giulio <66009328+lsd-cat@users.noreply.github.com>
Subject: [PATCH] net: ethernet: include Vega FisiLink switch driver

Pulls in drivers/net/ethernet/fisilink/ for the FSL91030M switch fabric
driver, provided via files-6.12.

Signed-off-by: giulio <66009328+lsd-cat@users.noreply.github.com>
---

--- a/drivers/net/ethernet/Kconfig
+++ b/drivers/net/ethernet/Kconfig
@@ -72,6 +72,7 @@ source "drivers/net/ethernet/dlink/Kconf
 source "drivers/net/ethernet/emulex/Kconfig"
 source "drivers/net/ethernet/engleder/Kconfig"
 source "drivers/net/ethernet/ezchip/Kconfig"
 source "drivers/net/ethernet/faraday/Kconfig"
+source "drivers/net/ethernet/fisilink/Kconfig"
 source "drivers/net/ethernet/freescale/Kconfig"
 source "drivers/net/ethernet/fujitsu/Kconfig"
 source "drivers/net/ethernet/fungible/Kconfig"
--- a/drivers/net/ethernet/Makefile
+++ b/drivers/net/ethernet/Makefile
@@ -39,6 +39,7 @@ obj-$(CONFIG_NET_VENDOR_EMULEX) += emule
 obj-$(CONFIG_NET_VENDOR_ENGLEDER) += engleder/
 obj-$(CONFIG_NET_VENDOR_EZCHIP) += ezchip/
 obj-$(CONFIG_NET_VENDOR_FARADAY) += faraday/
+obj-$(CONFIG_NET_VENDOR_FISILINK) += fisilink/
 obj-$(CONFIG_NET_VENDOR_FREESCALE) += freescale/
 obj-$(CONFIG_NET_VENDOR_FUJITSU) += fujitsu/
 obj-$(CONFIG_NET_VENDOR_FUNGIBLE) += fungible/
